{{nihongo|'''''Wow, The Kid Gang of  Bandits! '''''|ドラミちゃん アララ少年山賊団!|''Dorami-chan: Arara shounen sanzoku Dan''}} is a [[Doraemon]] anime short film. It premiered in theatres of Japan on March 9, 1991 alongside ''[[Doraemon: Nobita's Dorabian Nights]]''. The movie's original plot was written by Hiroshi Fujimoto and Motoo Abiko.

== Music ==
★ OPENING SONG: "[[Hello! Dorami-Chan]] by [[Yamano Satako]]

